<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="efficient-adj">efficient <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪ'fɪʃnt/    美 /ɪ'fɪʃnt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>有效率的；高效能的</strong></h4>
<p>able to do sth well without wasting time, money or energy
反 inefficient </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>an efficient secretary
高效率的秘书</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>fuel-efficient car / energy-efficient light bulbs
节能汽车/节能灯泡</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You must find a more efficient way of organizing your time.
你必须找到一个能更有效地安排时间的方法。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>efficiently /ɪ'fɪʃntli/ adv   </p>
<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>With online shopping increasingly popular, the Internet is seen as a (n) <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (高效率的) way of reaching target customers.  （2014 福建改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. efficient  </p></div>